[COLOR red][B]Version 2.1.41[/B][/COLOR]
- Added "Anime" as a Search menu. Only anime results will appear. Similarly, the regular "TV Show" search menu will now exclude anime results.
- Added "Anime" as a Favorites menu. Only anime results will appear. Similarly, the regular "TV Show" favorites menu will now exclude anime results.
- Added Vietnamese to language options.
- Added "Use Weighted Value for Size Sorting" to Settings->Results->Sorting and Filtering. Enable this and Fen Light will weight HEVC file sizes as being equal to 2x a non-HEVC file size for purposes of sorting (not filtering).
- Other changes/fixes.


